# UI Component [Web Image Search] V1.0
### Usage
- Search a static image from Internet with a keyword
- Search a moving gif image from Internet with a keyword

### UI Elements
- **Actionbar**:
  - Input Box: Input search keyword 
  - Clean Input Button: Clean the input texts
  - Button: Back
  - Button: Done

- **Tab Bar**:
  - Tab Bar: Input search keyword 
  - Button: Gif image search
  - Button: Static image search

- **Search Result List** : 
  - A two columns grid list view for gif image result
  - A three columns grid list view for static image result

- **Popup Keyboard**:
  - Button: Search 
  
### Behaviors 
- **Actionbar_Back {Tap}** : 
  - Go back to previous page without the picked image
- **Actionbar_Done {Tap}** : 
  - Go back to previous **[[ImagePicker]](https://hackmd.io/KwBgLAHMCGCMBGBaAzAYwOxkWAbAEwFNFp4RUUJ5loBOYVaMdHIA)** with the picked image
  - The picked image will be temporarily saved in the latest position on  **[[ImagePicker]](https://hackmd.io/KwBgLAHMCGCMBGBaAzAYwOxkWAbAEwFNFp4RUUJ5loBOYVaMdHIA)** appears as selected status
- **Actionbar_InputBox {Tap}** : 
  - Focus on the input box and popup the keyboard
  - Dropdown from the input box show three previous searched keywords
- **Tapbar_Gif {Tap}** : 
  - Display the gif image search view
- **Tapbar_Image {Tap}** : 
  - Display the static image search view
- **PopupKeyboard_Search {Tap}**:
  - Commit search action
  - **[On Error]** when the Internet connection is lost return No Result notice
- **SearchResultList_Cell {Tap}** : 
  - Tap to select the image in cell 
  - When selected has a sim-tranparent overlay with a number of the select sequence on it
  - When tap again the selected cell deselect the cell
  - The max number of the image can be picked in one go is 10
  - **[On Error]** when selecting an image exceeded the selection limit, popup a dialog box to notice the user
  
